Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.74,0:21:26.61,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.65,0:21:31.22,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在伙伴当中是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:34.34,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}绝不会让给别人
